        public Integer getOpCode()
        Get the operation code corresponding to the nature of the sent message.
        Returns:
        The operation code: 0(normal), 1(WebSocket connection opened), 2(replay done and ready to resume), 8(invalid lastMessageId), or 9(unknown)
